stream
BT
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 738 Tm
13 TL
(4. A lightweight screening head or scoring layer turns embeddings into model outputs.) Tj
T*
(5. If the transformer stack is unavailable, the application falls back to heuristic features so the dashboard still functions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 3. Audio Models) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 3.1 wav2vec2) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**What it is**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(wav2vec2 is a self-supervised speech representation model. It learns from raw audio waveforms instead of requiring hand-crafted acoustic features only.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Working principle**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- The audio waveform is encoded into latent speech representations.) Tj
T*
(- The model learns patterns from speech structure using contrastive objectives.) Tj
T*
(- During fine-tuning, the learned speech features are adapted to transcription or classification tasks.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Why it matters in this project**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Speech is important in rural screening because many users may prefer voice input over typing. wav2vec2 helps the system understand speech from Bengali and Hindi speakers, including dialect variation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**How the project uses it**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The repository supports wav2vec2 as a fine-tuning family for rural speech. It can be configured for dialect-specific training and uses local cached checkpoints when available.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Typical use cases in this repo:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- speech-to-text transcription) Tj
T*
(- dialect-aware adaptation) Tj
T*
(- transcription support for downstream mental health screening) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 3.2 Whisper) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**What it is**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Whisper is a multilingual speech recognition model that maps audio to text using an encoder-decoder architecture.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Working principle**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- The audio is converted into a learned representation.) Tj
T*
(- The decoder generates the transcript token by token.) Tj
T*
(- The model is trained on large and diverse speech-text pairs, which makes it robust to accents, noise, and varied speaking styles.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Why it matters in this project**) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
